title: ISplitLineFeatureData.IGetContours
description: Gets the selected contours for this split line feature.
returns: in-process, unmanaged C++: Pointer to an array of contours of these types: Sketch contour Sketch region VBA, VB.NET, C#, and C++/CLI: Not supported See In-process Methods for details about this type of method.
remarks:
Call
ISplitLineFeatureData::GetContoursCount
before calling this method to determine the size of the array for this method.
See
Accessing Selections that Define Features
for additional details.
